=============
Version 0.1.6
=============

Bugs Fixed
==========
- Accerciser now blocks SIGSTP so the entire desktop won't hang (bug
#457965). Thanks Simos Xenitellis!
- Fixed bookmark management.
- Other tiny bug fixes.

